		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="ro" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><table class="infocaseta"><tbody><tr><td colspan="2" class="antet autor" style="background-color:#4C6099;color:#FFFFFF;">Gheorghe Șincai</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="text-align:center"><a href="/wiki/Fi%C8%99ier:Gheorghe_Sincai_-_Foto01.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Gheorghe Sincai - Foto01.jpg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fe/Gheorghe_Sincai_-_Foto01.jpg/200px-Gheorghe_Sincai_-_Foto01.jpg" decoding="async" width="200" height="267" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fe/Gheorghe_Sincai_-_Foto01.jpg/300px-Gheorghe_Sincai_-_Foto01.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fe/Gheorghe_Sincai_-_Foto01.jpg/400px-Gheorghe_Sincai_-_Foto01.jpg 2x" data-file-width="450" data-file-height="600"></a></td></tr><tr><th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;background-color:#4C6099;color:#FFFFFF;">Date personale</th></tr><tr><th style=";">Născut</th><td colspan="1" class="" style=";"><a href="/wiki/28_februarie" title="28 februarie">28 februarie</a> <a href="/wiki/1754" title="1754">1754</a><span style="display:none">(<span class="bday">1754-02-28</span>)</span><br><a href="/wiki/R%C3%A2ciu_de_C%C3%A2mpie" class="mw-redirect" title="Râciu de Câmpie">Râciu de Câmpie</a>, <a href="/wiki/Comitatul_Turda_(Torda)" title="Comitatul Turda (Torda)">Comitatul Turda</a><br><span style="display:inline;vertical-align:baseline"><span style="display:inline-block;margin:2px 0px;vertical-align:baseline;border:solid 1px #AAAAAA;border-collapse:collapse;padding:0px 0px"><a href="/wiki/Fi%C8%99ier:Flag_of_the_Habsburg_Monarchy.svg" class="image"><img alt="Flag of the Habsburg Monarchy.svg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7a/Flag_of_the_Habsburg_Monarchy.svg/20px-Flag_of_the_Habsburg_Monarchy.svg.png" decoding="async" width="20" height="13" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7a/Flag_of_the_H